        {
            "id": 6009680,
            "title": "東陽5月營收創逾1年來低 關稅和匯率使AM需求趨觀望",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>汽車零組件東陽 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1319:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1319\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1319-TW</a>) 今 (6) 日公布 5 月合併營收 18.02 億元，月減 22.97%，年減 16.05%，創 2024 年 3 月以來低點，東陽不諱言，AM 需求受到關稅和匯率之亂等影響，客戶態度轉趨觀望。</p></section><p></p><div class=\"c1hvmcli\"><figure><div class=\"iirgi4a\"><img alt=\"cover image of news article\" class=\"cr8g41v\" data-nimg=\"fill\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" sizes=\"\n            (max-width: 1024px) 100% 406px,\n            (max-width: 768px) 100% 193px\n          \" src=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75\" srcset=\"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=16&amp;q=75 16w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=32&amp;q=75 32w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=48&amp;q=75 48w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=64&amp;q=75 64w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=96&amp;q=75 96w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=128&amp;q=75 128w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=256&amp;q=75 256w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=384&amp;q=75 384w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=640&amp;q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=750&amp;q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=828&amp;q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=1080&amp;q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=1200&amp;q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=1920&amp;q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=2048&amp;q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcimg.cnyes.cool%2Fprod%2Fnews%2F6009680%2Fl%2F04813101032afd1b2f86251448f6a45e.jpg&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 3840w\" style=\"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent\"/></div><figcaption class=\"c1gcnfq1\">東陽持續拓展北美AM版圖中。(鉅亨網資料照)</figcaption></figure></div><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>東陽前 5 月合併營收 114.32 億元，年增 10%。</p></section><section>\n</section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>由於對等關稅對需求造成衝擊，東陽 AM 事業 5 月合併營收 13.23 億元，月減 27%，年減 18%，前 5 月合併營收 88.94 億元，年增 14%，仍創史上前 5 月新高紀錄。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>東陽說明，AM 市場處傳統淡季，再加上關稅、匯率之亂等不確定性因素影響，客戶轉趨觀望，將持續專注本業，讓競爭力做到最具優勢。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>目前東陽台南科工廠積極趕工中，力拚下半年完工，七股科工區已於 5 月底動工建廠，計畫於 2026 年底完工，而美國德州廠也持續加緊腳步擴廠建設，為 AM 市場未來 3-5 年成長需求做好準備。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>而東陽 OEM 事業 5 月合併營收 4.79 億元，年減 8%，前 5 月合併營收 25.38 億元，將持續整理整頓、汰弱留強，提升整體 OEM 競爭力。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
